'Bird' Award Winners: American tenor saxophonist Stan Getz, 63, and Belgian 
guitarist Philip Catherine, 48, won the "Bird" jazz prize Wednesday, awarded 
annually to an American and a non-American at the North Sea Jazz Festival in 
The Hague, Netherlands. 
</P>
