DIANNE; CALIFORNIA -- ELECTIONS -- 1990; PRIMARY ELECTIONS; POLITICAL 
CAMPAIGNS; POLITICAL CANDIDATES; WILSON, PETE; CALIFORNIA GOVERNOR 
</P>
