</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By CAROL WATSON 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A Simi Valley woman was in custody Thursday on suspicion of setting fire to her 
house, police said. 
</P>
