<P>
BASKETBALL TOURNAMENTS; NATIONAL COLLEGIATE ATHLETIC ASSOCIATION; UNIVERSITY OF 
CONNECTICUT; COLLEGE ATHLETICS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA032390-0127 </DOCNO>
