<P>
Photo, Noy Sundara is favored to win Southern Section singles title. GLENN 
KOENIG / Los Angeles Times; Photo, COLOR, (C1) TOP OF HER GAME: Noy Sundara of 
Buena Park heads into badminton season as a top contender for the Southern 
Section singles title. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
