<P>
One day after reporting the end of a romance between billionaire Donald Trump 
and a former beauty queen, a New York newspaper today said Trump's friend 
secretly lived for weeks in the same building as his wife and children. 
</P>
<P>
The Daily News said Trump had hidden Marla Maples in his luxurious Trump Tower 
building in mid-town Manhattan. 
</P>
<P>
