said. On Thursday, the News and the New York Post reported that the alleged 
romance between Trump, 43, and Maples was over. Sources close to Trump's 
glamorous 41-year-old wife reportedly told the News that Ivana will file court 
papers Monday that will lay claim to half of Trump's vast empire. 
